### UI

#### [NEW] [tts_tab.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/tts_tab.py)

**Layout:**
```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Scan Folder  │  Add Files  │  Lang: [en] │
│ Tier: [flash▼] Threads: [4] Output: [...] │
├──────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ 📁 folder_name (3)                       │
│   ✅ en_001_Chapter 1.txt         1500w  │
│   ✅ en_002_Chapter 2.txt         1200w  │
│   ✅ en_003_Chapter 3.txt         1800w  │
│ 📁 another_folder (2)                    │
│   ✅ en_001_Chapter 1.txt         1400w  │
│   ✅ en_002_Chapter 2.txt         1600w  │
├──────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ All │ None │ Clear │ Process │ Stop │    │
│ Retry │ Open │                           │
└──────────────────────────────────────────┘
│ [Log panel]                              │
```

**Xử lý:**
- Scan/Add → tree view nhóm theo folder
- Process → multi-thread gửi AI cleanup từng file
- Output: `{output_dir}/{lang}_tts_{original_name}.txt`
- Retry: xử lý lại các file lỗi
- Status column: `—` / `Processing` / `✓ Done` / `❌ Error`

